Our popular RAV4 adds rugged good looks, too, with LED lighting, fog lamps, 17-inch alloy wheels, dual chrome exhaust outlets, and a rear spoiler for a sporty finish.Our XLE cabin encourages you to take command of each day with supportive fabric seats, eight-way power for the driver, a multifunction steering wheel, dual-zone climate control, and high-tech benefits that are anchored by an Entune infotainment system. Enjoy bold style for every mile in our RAV4 XLE! Low Hassle Pricing means that you dont have to be an expert negotiator to get a good, fair deal on your next used vehicle.
